Unit and regression tests for x.py
==================================

Motivation
----------
Code in x.py can currently not be subjected to testing for unit and regression testing and continuous integration.

Goal & Requirements
-------------------
The primary functional goal of this task is to be able test x.py for regressions and continuous integration.

Approach
--------
To meet the task goal, x.py needs to implement an additional command for self tests.
This command shall execute nose to execute test functions.
The implementation may support test functions in x.py itself or in a separate test file.
